Package com.karusmc.xmc.xml

Provides classes that handles parsing XML files.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClosableXMLEventReader
    A wrapper class for XMLEventReader that implements the AutoClosable interface to allow for a XMLEventReader instance to be used in try-with resource statements.
    Parser
    Provides XML document parsing capabilities to other classes.
    ParserBuilder
    Convenience class that provides other classes with pre-configurated parsers for parsing the commands.xml and configuration.xml files.
    ParserRegister
    Acts as the base command for use in a Parser instance.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ParserException
    Exception that is thrown when an error has occurred while parsing an XML file.

Package com.karusmc.xmc.xml Description

Provides classes that handles parsing XML files. This package includes a general-purpose XML parser, a static builder class which builds and configures the internally used parser instances and additional parsing related classes.
